WORLD OF WONDERS
The animal world is full of fascinating wonders.
Though Man is undoubtedly the most intelligent being on Earth, many animals have amazing talents and skills. Man has learnt many valuable lessons from them, too.
There are, among them, super tricksters, master builders, clever tool-users, and amazing hunters.
The unusual adaptations and abilities of animals never cease to surprise even the brightest scientists.
This issue of Tell Me Why is letting you take a small peep into this complex and mysterious world of wonders.
